'''飓风朱莉娅'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Julia}}）是有可靠卫星观测纪录以来在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]内形成位置最偏东面的[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|四级飓风]]<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510121046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | archivedate = 2015-05-10 | format = TXT | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-050515.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-05-07 | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，也是[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第12个热带气旋，第5场飓风和第4场大型飓风。系统于9月12日由[[佛得角|佛得角]]附近的[[东风波|东风波]]迅速发展形成，从该群岛附近经过，很快就于次日达到热带风暴标准并获名“朱莉娅”（{{lang|en|Julia}}）。9月14日，气旋达到飓风标准并马上进入[[快速增强|爆发性增强期]]，仅用24小时就从飓风强度下限增强至四级飓风下限。达到最高强度后，朱莉娅因同附近的[[飓风伊戈尔|飓风伊戈尔]]相互影响导致未能进一步发展，再于9月18日降级成热带风暴。接下来气旋行经海域[[海面温度|水温]]逐渐降低，外界环境渐趋不利。9月20日，朱莉娅开始转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，气象机构在这时停止对其发布公告。

飓风朱莉娅自始至终都没有对任何陆地构成显著威胁，因此引发的破坏很小。佛得角群岛南部有间歇性降水，引发局部轻度洪灾和少许不便。当地阵风时速最高为48公里，对农作物造成少量伤害。此外，气旋还导致海况恶劣，大浪对多个岛的海岸沿线构成威胁。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Julia 2010 track.png}}
飓风朱莉娅源于9月11日离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]的一股强劲[[东风波|东风波]]，其中保有深层[[对流|对流]]和强劲的东风<ref name="TCR">{{cite web | title = Hurricane Julia Tropical Cyclone Report | date = 2010-12-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025074352/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL122010_Julia.pdf | last1 = Beven | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL122010_Julia.pdf | accessdate = 2012-10-25 | first1 = Jack | last2 = Landsea | first2 = Christopher | publisher = National Hurricane Center | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>，促使[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始对其进行追踪<ref name="outlook1">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044323/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009111151/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009111151 | last1 = Blake | first1 = Eric | last2 = Brennan | first2 = Michael | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009111151/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009111151 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2010-09-11 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-04}}</ref>。东风波以每小时16至24公里的速度保持总体向西移动，其组织结构迅速改善，海面气压也显著降低<ref name="outlook3">{{cite web | date = 2010-09-12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009111738/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009111738 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044342/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009111738/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009111738 | author = Kimberlain, Todd; Beven, Jack | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>。经过数小时的继续组织，美国国家飓风中心认为东风波发展成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]的可能性仅有小幅提升<ref name="special">{{cite web | author = Kimberlain, Todd; Beven, Jack | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2010-09-12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044359/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009120301/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009120301 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009120301/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009120301}}</ref>。到了9月12日，热带低气压已经形成，美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]当天下午15点开始针对位于[[佛得角|佛得角]]群岛最南端东南方向约400公里洋面的气旋发布公告<ref name="advis1">{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.001.shtml? | last = Brennan | first = Michael | title = Tropical Depression Advisory Number One | date = 2010-09-12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024224405/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.001.shtml | archivedate = 2012-10-24}}</ref>。

接下来数小时里，低气压继续向西移动并稳步增强。美国国家飓风中心在实际操作中是于9月13日清晨将低气压升级成热带风暴并以“朱莉娅”（{{lang|en|Julia}}）为其命名，但之后经过重新分析确认，成为热带低气压仅12小时后，气旋风速就已达到每小时65公里<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="advis3">{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044510/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.003.shtml? | last = Brown | first = Daniel | title = Tropical Storm Julia Advisory Number Three | date = 2010-09-13 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。朱莉娅的强度在从佛得角附近经过的数小时里没有显著变化，不过风暴逐渐沿[[高压脊|深层高压脊]]的南部边缘回转向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动。绕过佛得角群岛后，气旋恢复缓慢增强势头，到9月14日清晨，[[气象卫星|卫星图像]]显示其中已有不规则的长条形[[风眼|眼状特征]]形成。<ref name="TCR" />朱莉娅行经海域局部出现28[[摄氏度|°C]]的高[[海面温度|海面温度]]，风暴随之进入[[快速增强|快速增强]]期，仅数小时后就达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准<ref name="advis8">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.008.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044515/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.008.shtml | last = Cangialosi | first = John | title = Hurricane Julia Advisory Number Eight | date = 2010-09-14 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-05 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。虽然所处洋面的[[海洋热含量|海洋热含量]]相对较低，但因[[风切变|垂直风切变]]少、海面温度高，飓风仍在快速强化<ref name="TCR" />，于9月15日升级成二级飓风<ref name="advis11">{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044520/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.011.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.011.shtml? | last = Berg | first = Robbie | title = Hurricane Julia Advisory Number Eleven | date = 2010-09-15 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>，然后又在不到两小时后达到三级飓风标准，成为[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年大西洋飓风季]]的第4场[[热带气旋风级|大型飓风]]<ref name="advis12">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.012.shtml? | last1 = Cangialosi | first1 = John | last2 = Pasch | first2 = Richard | title = Hurricane Julia Special Advisory Number Twelve | date = 2010-09-15 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-05 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044526/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.012.shtml | deadurl = no}}</ref>。急剧强化的趋势仍在继续，气旋又在6小时后成为四级飓风<ref name="advis13">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025044536/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.013.shtml? | last = Cangialosi | first = John | title = Hurricane Julia Advisory Number Thirteen | date = 2010-09-15 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-05 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>。根据卫星数据估算，朱莉娅达到的[[最大持续风速|最高风速]]为每小时220公里，最低[[气压|气压]]948[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.99[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），不过美国国家飓风中心在实际操作中的估算值分别为每小时215公里和950毫巴（百帕，28.05英寸汞柱）<ref name="advis13" /> 。

达到最高强度时，朱莉娅沿[[冷心低压|中到上层低气压]]回转向西北方向前进，移动速度略有加快。这片中到上层低气压还在高空产生不利的南向气流，令风暴强度略有减弱。到了9月16日清晨，卫星图像上已经难以分辨气旋风眼，朱莉娅的强度下滑至低于大型飓风标准。在此期间，飓风同附近深层高压脊边缘的东南偏南转向气流结合，前进方向进一步朝西偏移。<ref name="TCR" />气旋的覆盖范围相对较小，强度仍达到飓风标准。接下来朱莉娅行进至规模更大的飓风伊戈尔东侧，朱莉娅的环流开始受到伊戈尔产生的外流冲击，再加上海面温度降低，朱莉娅的强度于9月17日晚降至低于飓风强度。此后，朱莉娅围绕持续不断的高压脊进一步迂回向北加速移动，<ref name="TCR" />几乎与伊戈尔完全合并。之后的几小时内，朱莉娅逐渐北上，然后转向东北，再又转朝东面行进。9月18日，朱莉娅的下层中心在向东移动期间部分暴露出来，但此后几小时里又有对流逐渐在中心上空重新发展出来。<ref name="TCR" />风暴内虽然还保有深层对流，但上空的垂直风切变却再度增长，导致风暴开始转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。估计朱莉娅于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月20日下午18点在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以西约1750公里洋面退化成不含热带天气系统特征的低气压区。<ref name="advis34">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.034.shtml? | last = Franklin | first = James | title = Tropical Storm Julia Advisory Number Thirty-four | date = 2010-09-20 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025051922/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al12/al122010.public.034.shtml | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>低气压区在大西洋上空蜿蜒行进了数日，起初继续保持向东移动的趋势，然后又以环状路径南下。朱莉娅的残留飘忽不定地前进，一度向西北方向移动到距[[百慕大|百慕大]]563公里海域，美国国家飓风中心再次对之进行监控。但由于外界环境不利，系统未能重新发展成热带气旋<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Pasch | first1 = Richard | last2 = Cangialosi | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025051930/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009271738/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009271738 | first2 = John | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2010-09-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009271738/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009271738 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>，对流也已经完全消亡，美国国家飓风中心于9月28日中止监控<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | last = Blake | first = Erik | date = 2010-09-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009281737/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009281737 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025051947/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009281737/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009281737}}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Igor_Julia_Karl_sept_16_2010_1445Z.jpg|thumb]]
朱莉娅发展成热带低气压时就立即对佛得角构成威胁。预计群岛降雨量至少会有76至127毫米，局部地区累计达203毫米。佛得角政府为此向南部群岛发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，影响范围包括[[马约岛|马约岛]]、[[圣地亚哥岛_(佛得角)|圣地亚哥岛]]、[[福戈岛|福戈岛]]和[[布拉瓦岛|布拉瓦岛]]。<ref name="advis1" />

风暴自始至终位于海上，没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]过任何陆地，因此没有任何报道表明气旋有造成任何人员伤亡或重大破坏。风暴逼近期间，佛得角南部有间歇性降水和阵风，风速在每小时38至48公里之间<ref name="Impact">{{cite web | author = Lusa | publisher = Radiotelevisão Caboverdiana | date = 2010-09-14 | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | title = Tempestade tropical Júlia afasta-se de Cabo Verde | url = http://www.rtc.cv/index.php?paginas=21&id_cod=1428 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5srVWWbeF?url=http://www.rtc.cv/index.php?paginas=21 | archivedate = 2010-09-19 }}</ref>。[[萨尔岛|萨尔岛]]测得的降雨量不足9.9毫米，是各岛仅有的雨量纪录<ref>{{cite web | author = Resident of Sal, Cape Verde | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2010-09-12 | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | archivedate = 2015-10-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151007090646/http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/GVAC/2010/9/12/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA | title = Weather History for Sal, Cape Verde: September 12, 2010 | url = http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/GVAC/2010/9/12/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Resident of Sal, Cape Verde | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2010-09-13 | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | title = Weather History for Sal, Cape Verde: September 13, 2010 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151007090852/http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/GVAC/2010/9/13/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA | archivedate = 2015-10-07 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/GVAC/2010/9/13/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA}}</ref>。风暴经过期间，有关部门取消了佛得角境内及国际间的多架航班<ref name="Impact" />。圣地亚哥岛因洪灾引发多起山体滑坡，导致局部地区同外界的交通中断，另有多个社区的[[玉米|玉米]]作物受损<ref>{{cite web | author = ACG | publisher = Expresso das Ilhas | date = 2010-09-13 | accessdate = 2010-10-23 | archivedate = 2010-10-23 | url = http://www.expressodasilhas.sapo.cv/pt/noticias/go/mau-tempo--estragos-no-interior-de-santiago-e-no-fogo | title = Mau Tempo: estragos no interior de Santiago e no Fogo | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5tgWcQV21?url=http://www.expressodasilhas.sapo.cv/pt/noticias/go/mau-tempo--estragos-no-interior-de-santiago-e-no-fogo | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Lusa | publisher = iOnline | date = 2010-09-13 | accessdate = 2010-09-19 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.ionline.pt/conteudo/78244-tempestade-julia-afasta-se-gradualmente-cabo-verde | title = Tempestade "Júlia" afasta-se gradualmente de Cabo Verde | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5srW9FfL3?url=http://www.ionline.pt/conteudo/78244-tempestade-julia-afasta-se-gradualmente-cabo-verde | archivedate = 2010-09-19 }}</ref>。此外，朱莉娅还令海上波涛汹涌，高3至4.5米的大浪导致多个岛上的海岸受到轻度干扰<ref name="Impact" />。

